@node "inst" "Getting this sod to work..."
(1) Copy all files to >NIL:

(2) Adjust the tooltypes as below:

SAFEPASS=The password select users can have to bypass everything.
         Note: 15 chars or less!

PRIVMAIL=Name of sysop for private alert message.

EALLCONF=Path to conf for EALL message. Must end with '/'

PRIVCONF=Path to conf for PRIV message. Must end with '/'

DROPLINE=yes/no - Ditch user from system if he's fucking about.

LOGOTEXT=Path/filename to main screen gfx file.

MAILTEXT=Path/filename for PRIV message header txt.

SENDEALL=yes/no - Alert board users of hack attempts.

LOWERAXS=yes/no - Lower a hacker's access level.

NUAXSLVL=The level to drop a user to if function enabled.

MAILSUBJ=Subject for all messages sent.

EALLTEXT=Path/filename for EALL message header txt.

@endnode
